Avoiding Fights Over Deposits
Most deposit hassles involve disputes over “How clean is clean?” or “What’s wear and tear?” Disputes over back rent or replacements are more rare. Unfortunately, no statute or court opinion will give you a universally accepted standard for cleanliness or “normal” wear and tear. Smart landlords




