About TVA









Contact Us

General Inquiries
Email us at tvainfo@tva.gov, or call our main line at (865) 632-2101. This number can connect you to any TVA employee or facility.
Corporate Offices
To be referred to any TVA department or employee, contact the office nearest you:
Knoxville
Tennessee Valley Authority 400 W. Summit Hill Dr. Knoxville, TN 37902 (865) 632-2101 
Chattanooga
Tennessee Valley Authority  1101 Market St.  Chattanooga, TN 37402 (423) 751-0011
Nashville
Tennessee Valley Authority One Century Plaza26 Century Blvd, Suite 100Nashville, TN 37214
Muscle Shoals
TVA ReservationP.O. Box 1010  Muscle Shoals, AL 35662 (256) 386-2601
Emergency Assistance
If there is immediate danger or you witness a crime on TVA property, first dial 911 from an outside line to request assistance from local authorities, then notify the TVA Police at (855) 476-2489 toll-free.
You can also call one of the monitoring and notification centers below:
Knoxville
(800) 824-3861 (toll-free) (865) 632-3631 (865) 632-4318 (TDD)
Chattanooga
(800) 548-4005 (toll-free) (423) 751-4005 (423) 751-2605 (TDD)













