Lake Levels


Is today a good day for boating, fishing or swimming on your favorite TVA reservoir? Here’s where you can get all the data you need to plan your day on the water.


Get the most up-to-date information on the individual reservoirs TVA manages, including observed and predicted elevations, planned generation releases at the dams, reservoir operating guides, ecological health ratings, fish population survey results, recreation facilities and more.
Choose any reservoir name, then click “View Info” to get the latest information for that reservoir.
NOTE: These values are updated throughout the day as conditions change, so check often.





